text: The Kazakh Wikipedia is the Kazakh-language edition of Wikipedia. This edition started in June 2002. It is the 33rd largest edition.Wikimedia list of Wikipedias and their statistics.. Retrieved 25 October 2015. As of July 2013, it had over 202,000 articles.List of Wikipedias on Meta-Wiki. ==References== ==Other websites== *Kazakh Wikipedia main page Category:Wikipedias Category:Websites established in 2002
